testRun.title: NetBeans IDE 8.0 Beta readiness check
testRun.desc:
Quick sanity test of NetBeans IDE 8.0 Beta candidate build #201401091443 [1]. Ideally use latest build of JDK 8 [2]. All testers are required to finish their testing by Monday - January 13th 8:00 AM UTC [3].

[1] http://bits.netbeans.org/netbeans/8.0/beta/w7ds4jn2
[2] https://jdk8.java.net/download.html
[3] http://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?iso=20140113T0800
